// COMMAND HANDLERS — All handlers wired to real production subsystems
// ============================================================================
// Subsystem APIs used: ModelInvoker, UnifiedHotpatchManager, DeterministicSwarmEngine,
// PerfTelemetry, BinaryAnalyzer, NativeDisassembler, RECodex, NativeCompiler,
